<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Zhe Wang</title><link href="/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="/feeds%5Czhe-wang.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>/</id><updated>2014-10-04T00:00:00+02:00</updated><entry><title>Simple steps to a personal blog</title><link href="/simple-steps-to-a-personal-blog.html" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2014-10-04T00:00:00+02:00</updated><author><name>Zhe Wang</name></author><id>tag:,2014-10-04:simple-steps-to-a-personal-blog.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;This personal blog is constructed on the following components:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://pages.github.com/"&gt;Github Pages&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="docs.getpelican.com"&gt;Pelican&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://help.github.com/articles/markdown-basics/"&gt;Markdown&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To start, one needs to set up a repository on Github&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$ make publish&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$ cd output&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$ git init&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$ git add --all&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$ git commit -m "the changes"&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$ git push https://github.com/zhwa/zhwa.github.io.git&lt;/p&gt;</summary></entry></feed>